{"title_en":"Huge ancient city discovered in the Amazon rainforest","title_bn":"????? ??????????? ????? ??????? ????? ??????","summary_en":"Archaeologists have discovered a 2,500-year-old urban network in the Ecuadorian Amazon using laser technology, revealing a more complex society than previously known.","summary_bn":"????????????????? ????? ????????? ??????? ??? ??????????? ?????? ?,??? ????? ????? ???? ??? ?????????? ???????? ??????, ?? ???? ?????? ???? ???? ????? ??????? ?????? ????","body_en":"A massive network of ancient cities has been discovered in the Amazon rainforest, dating back around 2,500 years. Using LiDAR (Light Detection and Ranging) technology, researchers mapped the Upano Valley in eastern Ecuador, revealing thousands of earthen mounds, plazas, and a complex road system. This discovery challenges the long-held belief that the Amazon was home only to small, nomadic tribes, showing instead a highly organized and densely populated society that existed long before the Inca Empire. The discovery includes structures for domestic, ceremonial, and agricultural use, spanning over a vast area that connects several major settlements.","body_bn":"????? ??????????? ????? ?,??? ??? ???? ?? ????? ??????? ????? ?????? ????? ????? ????????? ????? ???? ??????? ????? ???????? ????? (LiDAR) ????????? ??????? ??? ????????????????? ????? ????? ????? ????, ?????? ??? ???? ???? ??? ????????? ???????? ???? ??????? ?? ?????????? ????? ???????? ?????????? ????????? ????????? ?????????? ??? ??? ??? ????? ???? ??? ??? ?????? ?????? ??? ???? ??? ?????? ??? ?? ???? ??????????? ???? ???? ?????? ???? ??????? ???????? ??? ??????????? ???? ???? ?? ?????????? ????? ??????, ?????? ????-???????? ??? ????????? ???? ??????? ??????? ??????? ??????????? ????? ?? ????? ????? ???? ??????? ????","image_prompt_en":"An aerial 3D LiDAR visualization of an ancient city hidden beneath a dense green rainforest canopy, showing structured mounds, squares, and straight roads connecting various part